                <p>The airline has already removed single-use plastic from its onboard service. This is a great initiative by the airline, and now, you can’t find items like plastic straws, stir sticks, and cups that have been replaced with biodegradable or reusable alternatives. This move of the airline also reduces the airline's plastic waste by millions of items annually.</p>
