                <p>Yes, and this is the agenda of the airline right now. The airline is working toward the goal of achieving net-zero emissions by 2040. Other initiatives include Fuel-Efficient Aircraft: The introduction of Boeing 737 MAX aircraft reduces fuel consumption and emissions. Carbon Offsetting Programs: Encouraging passengers to participate in carbon offset initiatives during bookings.</p>
